{
  "stem": "3952.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A small, another funny situation that happened in the camp, in Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were working about-- this was like 10 days before-- before-- at the end of April in 1945.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This-- we were working outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were working on a platform where we were bringing-- we were building railways.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, a rail like this, we would catch like six people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Each one would pick it up and throw it down on the floor from the platform.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, I was so weak, I was weighing like 35 kilos at the time, which is like 75 pounds, I would say, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so weak that I couldn't withhold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was falling with that rail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Each rail that we picked up, I was falling with the rail.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the German who work-- was the overseer, would pick me up at the bottom of the pants like a bundle, and put me back on there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everybody would laugh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was so funny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And now, you think about it, how weak I was, and-- and this was a funny situation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were laughing about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I would like--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would like to tell about a very particular spiritual-- heightened spiritual experience that we had in-- that I had in camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was every Friday night after the meal, we would come into one of the tents, and we were singing zemirot songs, shabbat songs, with tears is running from our eyes.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the closeness to God that we felt, never before and never after have I felt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was always a very religious boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Never before and never after have I felt so close to God.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was visible and tangible.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
